title: Maria Callas - 10 CD's
description:
These are all .OGG format.   I have these on cd&#039;s burned in
.mp3 format - I love Total Audio Converter - it never fails me.
They were .OGG when I got them, but you lot all know what you
are doing.  So no problems for you.

It&#039;s 1950, and it&#039;s Mexico.

Tosca, Norma, Aida, Traviata, Trovatore.

My .mp3&#039;s tell me the bitrate is 192kbps.

I&#039;m going back to my booze now.   Laugh and the world
